218
00:23:49,400 --> 00:23:51,500
What are you staring at?

219
00:23:51,500 --> 00:23:54,300
Were you the girl from back then?

220
00:23:54,300 --> 00:23:57,600
Back then? What do you mean?

221
00:23:57,600 --> 00:24:00,600
