I could give you a free ride home.

253
00:27:15,300 --> 00:27:17,000
Never mind.

254
00:27:20,400 --> 00:27:22,200
This is my business card.

255
00:27:22,200 --> 00:27:25,000
Thank you for helping me out just now.

