00:27:38,200 --> 00:27:42,000
Consider this an IOU you gave me.

262
00:27:42,000 --> 00:27:43,600
Wait.

263
00:27:44,600 --> 00:27:46,500
May I know your name?

264
00:27:47,500 --> 00:27:49,200
Su Xieyi.

265
